00:00:20.439 --> 00:00:24.529
With the multi-player they've kind of made some changes here to the previous Killzone formula.

00:00:24.529 --> 00:00:26.419
It is a first person shooter still.

00:00:26.419 --> 00:00:30.710
But the idea of earning XP to unlock weaponry

00:00:30.710 --> 00:00:34.920
