00:00:51.260 --> 00:00:55.530
to set particular kind of scores by doing

00:00:55.530 --> 00:00:58.840
particular actions and then you unlock effectively like badges for it.

00:00:58.840 --> 00:01:02.220
So for instance you might have to kill 50 people with

00:01:02.220 --> 00:01:05.970
an assault rifle then kill 20 people with a grenade

00:01:05.970 --> 00:01:10.320
and then kill 10 people with a blade and that
will get you a particular

00:01:10.320 --> 00:01:13.500
achievement as it were. Now all of this
actually makes for

00:01:13.500 --> 00:01:17.560
quite a fun game because now gone is the trudge of

00:01:17.560 --> 00:01:20.840
trying to unlock the next weapon and so
on to get to the good stuff. Now

00:01:20.840 --> 00:01:25.430
