00:01:25.430 --> 00:01:28.490
then something like Call of Duty where
you know best gun wins

00:01:28.490 --> 00:01:31.790
a lot of the time. Now, you're going to
have to think

00:01:31.790 --> 00:01:35.430
while you're playing. All of the various
different classes as it were of which there's

00:01:35.430 --> 00:01:36.780
three of, there's the scout,

00:01:36.780 --> 00:01:40.260
the assault guy and the support guy and
essentially

00:01:40.260 --> 00:01:43.810
they all fulfil different roles and they have different power-ups like drones

00:01:43.810 --> 00:01:47.619
shields and so on and you're going to have
to use these well with your team if

00:01:47.619 --> 00:01:48.619
